Josh Gates, Heather Amaro, and Phil Torrres uncover the creepiest moments of Expedition X Season 10. They dig into Spike Island’s secret smuggling and ancient legends, chase wild UFO sightings in the Arctic, and investigate strange disappearances in Massachusetts’ Bridgewater Triangle.
